WEBVTT

00:00:00.171 --> 00:00:04.040
To be effective, you must develop four interdependent facets of CQ.

00:00:05.203 --> 00:00:11.538
Metacognitive CQ is your mental capability to acquire and understand cultural knowledge, verifying assumptions.

00:00:12.560 --> 00:00:15.026
Cognitive CQ is your general knowledge base.

00:00:16.028 --> 00:00:18.674
Motivational CQ is your persistence in adapting.

00:00:19.596 --> 00:00:23.245
Behavioral CQ is your capability to exhibit appropriate actions.
